html

HTML -Hypertext Markup Language

This provide the content for a webpage to be displayed.


tags -------- tags are the components of a document, that encloses an element and the content.


attributes --- used to add additional properties for html tags.

for ex: src,alt in img tag, style for anchor tag, href for anchor tag....

elements ------







