+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

Lists in Html 
     Lists are used to organize a set of related items.
            There are three types of lists
            unordered list - no specific order

            <ul>
            <li> </li>
            </ul>

            ordered list   - ordering is done here

            <ol>
            <li> </li>
            </ol>

            descriptive lists  - used to add descriptions to the terms

            <dl>
            <dt>coffee</dt>
            <dd>costs 50 euros</dd>
            </dl>

-------------------


+++++++++++++++++++++++++
	
		Tables

Tables are a structured way to organize the data in rows and columns.

tables consists of two parts

table head  -  Header row to say what column is going to be stored
table body  -  all the relevant data

	<table>
		<caption>Table Heading</caption>
        <thead>
            <th></th>
            <th></th>
        </thead>

        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td></td>
                <td></td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td></td>
                <td></td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>


